cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on Chinese zero pronoun resolution. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses deep reinforcement learning models to improve the performance of the zero pronoun resolution task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep neural network models for learning semantic information. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses neural network models for the task. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not deal with image or video data, but it is still possible as the paper uses deep learning models.
